Dreams will not come true unless you have worked hard to be ready for the challenges ahead . During the talk , Dr . Van_Pham from Salem_State_University , Massachusetts , USA will be talking about how to prepare yourself for the best educational experience abroad . Dr . Pham will share her insights from Vietnamese as well as American perspectives . Open to the public ( students and parents are both welcome . )
Speaker : Dr . Van_Pham is an associate professor of economics at Salem_State_University in Massachusetts , United_States of America . She is currently a Fulbright_Scholar at Fulbright_Economics_Teaching_Program in Ho_Chi_Minh_City . She was a student and a university lecturer in Vietnam before coming to the US to do her graduate studies and then teaching at university level .
